@node "Registration" "Module Administrator 1.05 english documentation/Registration"
@Prev "Thanks"
@Toc "Main"

-----------------------------------------------------------------------

                           MoA is ShareWare.

-----------------------------------------------------------------------


    This means if you are using 'MoA' please pay the ShareWare fee.


    There are different ways to pay the Shareware fee.
    For people outside Germany the most easy way might be
    to send a eurocheque or the money (20,- US Dollar) together
    with the registration-letter.
    If you include the money itself in your letter please
    wrap it an extra piece of paper !

    If you send a foreign-cheque you MUST add $10 (US-Dollar) to
    the registartion fee for my personal bank-costs.
    If you pay with a foreign cheque and DONT add the surcharge
    I will not process your registration.

